---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Nerio – App Support">
    <h1 class="mb-6">Nerio – App Support</h1>
    <p class="mb-10 text-lg">
        Nerio is an app that helps you analyze messaging conversations to better understand emotional patterns, communication signals, and relationship dynamics.
    </p>

    <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">Contact Support</h2>
        <p class="mb-2">If you have questions, feedback, or need support, you can contact us at:</p>
        <p>
            <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:sandi.peklaric@gmail.com" class="underline hover:text-gray-300">sandi.peklaric@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-semibold">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

        <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium">How does Nerio work?</h3>
            <p>Nerio analyzes conversation patterns and message flow to provide insights into emotional tone, communication balance, and potential relationship signals.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium">Which languages are supported?</h3>
            <p>Nerio supports conversation analysis in more than 100 input languages. The app interface is available in over 20 languages.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium">Does Nerio store my conversations?</h3>
            <p>Conversations are processed securely to provide insights and are not shared with third parties.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>
            You can read our Privacy Policy here:<br />
            <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1-2PjYTPlshGCm89YfRgspqjSJyall3te/view?usp=drive_link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline hover:text-gray-300 break-all">
                Privacy Policy
            </a>
        </p>
    </section>
</Layout>
